        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does caliche make fence work harder here?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. The USDA soil description for the Las Vegas series identifies shallow, carbonate-rich soils with petrocalcic characteristics, which affects how water behaves and how shallow systems perform."
